FORMAT: 1A

# Fidelo School - Enquiries

Create and update (simple) enquiries within Fidelo School.

# Allowed HTTPs requests
<table>
    <tr>
        <td>POST</td>
        <td>Create new enquiry</td>    
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>PATCH</td>
        <td>Update existing enquiry</td> 
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>GET</td>
        <td>Get an enquiry or search for existing enquiries</td> 
    </tr>
</table>

# Possible Server Responses
- 200 `OK` - The request was successful.
- 400 `Bad Request` - The request could not be understood or was missing required parameters.
- 500 `Internal Server Error` - Something went wrong internally.
- e0001 `Error` - Either the token is wrong or the IP is not stored with the Token.

# Field Error Codes (Status 400)
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>Code</th>
        <th>Description</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>REQUIRED_FIELD_MISSING</td>
        <td>Required field is missing in request.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>INVALID_FIELD</td>
        <td>Field does not exist in API.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>INVALID_VALUE</td>
        <td>Invalid value for field. This could be a mismatching ID for resources.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>INVALID_DATE</td>
        <td>Invalid date format.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td>INVALID_EMAIL</td>
        <td>Invalid e-mail format.</td>
    </tr>
       <tr>
        <td>INVALID_PHONE</td>
        <td>Invalid phone number format.</td>
    </tr>
</table>


